<body>
    <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Page</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our website!</p>
        <p>This website is designed to manage a list of courses. Users can view the list of courses, add new courses, and delete existing courses.</p>
        <p>The database server used for this website is MariaDB, which is a popular open-source relational database management system.</p>
    
        <h2>Project Steps:</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Set up Node.js and Express</li>
            <li>Create routes for home, add, and about pages</li>
            <li>Design and implement home page with course list</li>
            <li>Design and implement add page for adding new courses</li>
            <li>Create database schema for storing courses</li>
            <li>Implement functionality to add and delete courses</li>
            <li>Style pages to improve visual appeal</li>
            <li>Push code to github</li>
            <li>Deploy on Render</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
